prefsnologintext2: Suang log montok monimban paanangan nu.
prefs-tabs-navigation-hint: Bilin: Oguno soto ramok gibang om wanan do papanau id piolitan do tongo luak id rayat luak.
prefs-sections-navigation-hint: Bilin: Oguno soto Tab (luak) om it duo soto Shift + Tab do papanau piolit do langud paanangan.
prefs-description-personal: Ipapai poingkuro ko koimbulai, rumomut om miwara.
prefs-help-realname:
Songkopili no ih ngaran otopot.
Nung potoundaon, gunoon iri do ponokotondos toodo nu.
passwordtooshort: Sokukuri do kapaas kiharo {{PLURAL:$1|1 pimato|$1 tongopimato}}.
passwordtoolong: Kada kolobi do {{PLURAL:$1|1 pimato|$1 tongopimato}} ninaru do palapus.
password-substring-username-match: Palapus nu nuru amu pointalang id ngaran momoguno nu.
password-name-match: Kapaasnu mositi do pisuaion mantad ko ngaranmogunonu.
password-login-forbidden: Pogoduhan pomogunaan ngaran momoguno om kaatalib diti.
passwordincommonlist: Poingamung it boros papalapus pinosuang id rayat do palapus di angasaru kopio gunoon. Pilio' palapus di poinsuai-suai.
prefs-help-yourpassword: Poingiau ponogi'an tisangkap. Intaai $1 montok lobi tinatap.
tog-prefershttps: Toririmo do momoguno noputan di otingolig soira do sumuang
prefs-help-prefershttps: Paanangan diti oontok kosuanan nu kosuut.
prefs-user-downloaddata-info: Kopoilaan tisangkap ku mantad tiwaal diti
prefs-user-restoreprefs-info: Pogulio' ngawi paanangan tudan (id ngawi langud)
gender-unknown: Soira mamarait diya, gunoon do tusod it hogot opitanga tondusai soira milo
prefs-help-gender: Songkopili nopo do patatap paanangan diti. Pakayon ma dit tusod i gatang dau do mangalap dia, om mamarait dia doid wookon mamakai tondusai woyoboros dit kosudong. Kopoilaan diti nopo nga' montok ginumuan.
prefs-help-variant: Kakawo toi woyopimato aanangan nu popokito tonsi' do natad wiki diti.
tog-fancysig: Pokitono sain sobaagi do tikwiki (miampai aiso popioput automatik kumaa liwang momoguno nu)
prefs-signature-invalid-warning: Tandatunturu nu kaanu kanto popoimbulai do kobolingkahangan kumaa piipiro kakamot.
prefs-signature-invalid-new:
Au kotunud tandatunturu nu dondo.
Oguno nu pia nga' amu ko milo monimban gisom koontok nu kawagu.
prefs-signature-invalid-disallow: Au otunud tandatunturu nu dondo. Gisom poontokon nu, tandatunturu lalai maan guno'o soira manandalongon komi nu.
prefs-changeemail: Simbanai toi iduo poikatan lopot dorud.
prefs-help-email: Surat-i pasagaon do momili, nga gunoon iti montok do popoguli do kaatalib, nung olihuannu kaatalib
prefs-help-email-others: Milo nogi do momili ko nung mokiromut do tulun suai momoguno maya do noputan surat-i id bolikon momogunonu toi id bolikon bolotok. Awu iy pokitonon surat-i nu kumaa do momomoguno suai.
tog-requireemail: Pootodon e-mel montok monginwagu ''password'' soira katahak o e-mel om ngaran momoguno.
noemailprefs: Patatapo no kinoyonon surat-i id komoisoonnu mooi do poposikit kowo-woyo diti
emailnotauthenticated:
Au po notinduan ot poikatan lopot dorud nu.
Inggaa lopot dorud pootodon montok nonggo tiso komoyon sumusuut.
emailauthenticated: Notinduan no poikatan lopot dorud nu ontok $2 bobog ko$3.
tog-ccmeonemails: Atadai oku do dolinan di surat-i it pinaatodku montok momomoguno suai
tog-enotifwatchlistpages: Ponuratai-i oku soira do haro bolikon toi pail lisintanganku haro nokowolion
tog-enotifusertalkpages: Ponuratai-i oku soira kiharo kowolion id pibabarasan momomogunoku
tog-enotifminoredits: Ponuratai-i oku nogi do nung haro no idit tongokoro do bolikon om nogi tangapail
tog-enotifrevealaddr: Pokitono adiris surat-i-ku id kapahabaran surat-i
tog-diffonly: Kada pokitono suang bobolikon id siriba tongodip
tog-norollbackdiff: Kada pokitono diff kalapas kowonsoi o pomogulian suntingan
tog-showrollbackconfirmation: Pokitono o prom pongokunan soira monodos pongoput popoguli
tog-editsectiononrightclick: Pabanaro sikson mongidit momoguno todos golibang id sikson tuluon
tog-minordefault: Tandaai oinsanan niditan tokoro sobaagi do pongoiso
tog-forceeditsummary: Posoroho oku no maamaso poposuang pongintigasan suntingan kusung (toi ko' pongintigasan do momonsoi lalai mantad)
tog-useeditwarning: Poingato oku soira mongiduan dii bobolikon nopingalanan nga awu poh nokoopi
tog-previewonfirst: Pokitonon kokitanan maamaso tumimpuun do monyunting
tog-previewontop: Pokitono duluon-kokikitanai id pogulu kutak idit
tog-uselivepreview: Pokitonon kopokitanan pogulu miampai amu momuat kawagu bolikan
tog-usenewrc: Tinimungan nopingalanan maya bobolikon ii wagu kaalanai om lispintangan
tog-hideminor: Lisoko idit tokoro ih wagu kaalanai.
tog-hidepatrolled: Lisoko idit tinamangan ih wagu kaalanai
tog-newpageshidepatrolled: Polisoko bolikan tinamangan mantad sanarai bolikan kawawagu
tog-extendwatchlist: Pointongo koinsanai listamangan do popokito koinsanai pinongundolihon, okon ko iri kawawagu nopo
tog-watchlistunwatchlinks: Poruhango pananda pongintong/  okon ko pongintong potilombus ({{int:Watchlist-unwatch}}/{{int:Watchlist-unwatch-undo}}) montok mongintong bolikas di nokosimban (JavaScript gunoon montok fungsi togol)
tog-watchlisthideminor: Polisoko niditan tokoto mantad do lis piintangan
tog-watchlisthidebots: Polisoko niditan rinobot mantad do lis pintangan
tog-watchlisthideown: Polisoko niditanku mantad do lis piintangan
tog-watchlisthideanons: Polisoko niditan di momomoguno ingaa ngaran mantad id lis pintanganku
tog-watchlisthideliu: Polisoko niditan di momomoguno sinumuang log mantad lis piintanganku
tog-watchlistreloadautomatically: Muat kawagu sanarai pongintangan miampai automatik monikid sumimban o panapis (minog do JavaScript)
tog-watchlisthidepatrolled: Polisoko niditan '''patrolled''' mantad do lis piintangan
tog-watchdefault: Ruhangai bolikon om tangapail di niditku id lisintanganku
tog-watchmoves: Ruhangai bolikon om tangapail di pinawalihku id lisintanganku.
tog-watchdeletion: Ruhangai bolikon om tangapail di pinugasku id lisintanganku
tog-watchcreations: Ruhangai bolikon di winonsoiku om nogi pail pinosuangku id lisintanganku
tog-watchuploads: Ruhangai fail wagu di nokosuang ku id katayadan pongintangan
tog-watchrollback: Ruhangai bolikan di pinotonduli ku id suang katayadan pongintangan ku
